welcome_message_body: "Welcome to DeForest, where the charm of small-town America meets endless outdoor adventures. Get ready to discover the area's natural beauty, rich history, and friendly community. Enjoy your stay and make the most of all that DeForest has to offer!"

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Dane County Regional Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A at Dane County Regional Airport serves primarily domestic flights.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B at Dane County Regional Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network by selecting 'MSN Airport WiFi' from their device's list of available networks.
